   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1903_AS_RBH_1_00038"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr Richard
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb173" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Rodaun bei Liesing</hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb40101"><hi rend="latintype">Liesinger Straße 2</hi></rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1903_AS_RBH_1_00040"/><hi rend="underline" n="1"><date>Donner<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date></hi>.</dateline><salute>lieber Richard,</salute></opener><p>könnte man<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich vielleicht <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01306-1"/><date>Sam<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01306-1"><ref target="1903-08-08" subtype="See" type="schnitzler-tagebuch"/>.
               </note> zum Nachtmahl in dem <rs type="place" ref="#pmb304">Hietzinger <hi rend="latintype">Restaurant</hi></rs> treffen? Vorher <rs type="place" ref="#pmb21799">Schönbrunn</rs>? <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb11740">Hugo</rs></hi> desgleichen<unclear>?</unclear></p><p>Schreiben Sie mir bitte ein Wort <pb facs="1903_AS_RBH_1_00041"/>Stund und Ort zu
               fixiren (<rs type="place" ref="#pmb50941">Glashaus</rs>? <time>Sieben</time>?)
               Schlechtes Wetter<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ollte (in Hin<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>icht aufs <hi rend="latintype">Rest.</hi>) kein
               Hindernis<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ein.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<lb/>Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur</signed></closer><postscript><p><pb facs="1903_AS_RBH_1_00041"/>Wenn Sie telephoniren bitte am be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ten 2–3.</p></postscript></div>
      </body>
